        Parameters:
        refInfo - Information about the strong and serialized references to the image.
        imageInfo - Image-specific information, e.g. memory consumption.
        imageSource - Description of source from which the ImageRef was created. Non-null only if detailed profiling has been previously enabled by a call to enableDetailedProfiling.
